WEBVTT

00:01.258 --> 00:03.768
That you're gonna have some ups and you're gonna have some downs.

00:05.695 --> 00:07.815
Most people give up on themselves easily.

00:08.002 --> 00:10.199
You know, the human spirit is powerful?

00:10.845 --> 00:12.054
There's nothing as powerful.

00:12.135 --> 00:14.369
It's hard to kill the human spirit!

00:15.758 --> 00:19.257
Anybody can feel good when they have their health, their bills are paid,...

00:19.515 --> 00:20.981
...they have happy relationships.

00:21.193 --> 00:23.193
Anybody could be positive then.

00:23.841 --> 00:27.931
The real challenge of growth, mentally, emotionally and spiritually,...

00:28.361 --> 00:30.618
...comes when you get knocked down.

00:32.159 --> 00:34.107
It takes courage to act.

00:35.790 --> 00:38.320
Part of being hungry when you've been defeated.

00:39.419 --> 00:43.296
It takes courage to start over again.

